This is a "plugin" for the Video Disk Recorder (VDR).

Written by:                  Alexander Grothe <seahawk1986@gmx.de>

Project's homepage:          https://github.com/seahawk1986/vdr-plugin-websocket/

Latest version available at: https://github.com/seahawk1986/vdr-plugin-websocket/

